T1  - CREDIT RATIONING, RISK AVERSION, AND INDUSTRIAL EVOLUTION IN DEVELOPING COUNTRIES
AU  - Bond, Eric W.
AU  - Tybout, James
AU  - Utar, Hale
Y1  - 2015/08/01
PY  - 2015
DA  - 2015/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12119
