T1  - REGULATION, IMPERFECT COMPETITION, AND THE U.S. ABORTION MARKET
AU  - Beauchamp, Andrew
Y1  - 2015/08/01
PY  - 2015
DA  - 2015/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12128
T2  - International Economic Review
